{"lemma":"تَخَلُّصاتٌ","slug":"تَخَلُّصاتٌ","root":"خ.ل.ص","root_slug":"خ-ل-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ل-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n11269"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AA%D9%8E%D8%AE%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%8F%D9%91%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rid, to get rid of","examples":[{"text":"تَخَلَّصَ مِنَ ٱلْأَعْرَاضِ فَقَطْ.","english":"He only got rid of the symptoms."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"liberation, freedom, extrication"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ta.xal.la.sˤa/","/ta.xal.lusˤ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n11269","headword_ar":"تخلّص","root":"xlS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became saved, secured,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"freed; he escaped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"freed himself;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became safe, secure, free,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a state of freedom"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"immunity;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) from a thing; (S;) as, for instance, a gazelle, and a bird, from a snare, (A,) [and a man from embarrassment or difficulty, or destruction, like as a thing becomes cleared from its turbidness, (see 1,) or] like spun thread when it has been entangled. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nasaba","text_ar":"نَسَبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlomaroA^api","text_ar":"بِالْمَرْاَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}